{"tid":2009891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有「伕名」只有林夕","createTime":"2020-05-10T05:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T05:45:15.000Z","uid":349563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59f6e997835c3fc74d6d53177c5128d01f2f6db5","tid":2009891,"uid":349563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"你跟香港的距離從不是台灣與香港的里程，那只是一趟機票的距離，你一直都在我們身邊。因此不用自責，不用再做那「內疚怪」<br />\n<br />\n思想是無法被褫奪的，你的「第一生命」並不會因為被伕名而快速消逝。我們會記得你是林夕，不是伕名。<br />\n就讓我們一起舉傘一起的撐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxuH39F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxuH39F.jpg&h=7b333b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲末睇既唔該你地去睇吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EoBORUgi6HA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEoBORUgi6HA&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=f82ba1bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EoBORUgi6HA</a>"},{"pid":"0dbd18f4e84ee4804de0ba67c1ba4e0bae0b5a2d","tid":2009891,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"「佚名」定「伕名」？"},{"pid":"163120b543dd57c9d936d097a638655c16017938","tid":2009891,"uid":349563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0dbd18f4e84ee4804de0ba67c1ba4e0bae0b5a2d","tid":2009891,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"「佚名」定「伕名」？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T05:45:15.000Z","msg":"Sor 自膠 <br />\n佚名"}]}